    ./in.cue:17:9
[eval] e0: invalid operands 2 and "a" to '+' (type int and string):
    ./in.cue:24:5
    ./in.cue:24:9
[eval] e5: cannot use 1.0 (type float) as int in argument 1 to div:
    ./in.cue:25:9
[eval] e6: cannot use 2.0 (type float) as int in argument 2 to rem:
    ./in.cue:26:12
